"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rt\"><code>&lt;rt&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rtc\"><code>&lt;rtc&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>S\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/s\"><code>&lt;s&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\"><code>&lt;samp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/spacer\"><code>&lt;spacer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sumário","title":"Sumário","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O <strong>Elemento&nbsp;HTML &lt;ol&gt;</strong>&nbsp;(ou<em> Elemento&nbsp;HTML de lista ordenada</em>) representa uma lista de itens ordenados. De forma característica esses itens&nbsp;ordenados em uma lista são mostrados com uma contagem que os precede, que pode ser de qualquer tipo, como numerais, letras, algarismos romanos, ou simples símbolos. Esse modelo numerado não é definido na descrição html da página, mas na folha de estilos CSS associada, pela propriedade<code> </code><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/list-style-type\"><code>list-style-type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Não há limitação para a&nbsp;profundidade&nbsp;e a imbricação das listas definidas com os elementos<code>&nbsp;</code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code></a><code> </code>e<code> </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\"><strong>Nota de uso: </strong>Ambos os&nbsp;elementos<code> </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code></a><code> </code>e<code> </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a>, representam uma lista de itens. Diferem porque, com o elemento<code>&nbsp;</code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code></a>,<code> </code>a ordem é significativa. Como regra de ouro para determinar qual deles usar, tente mudar a ordem dos itens da lista; se a significação for alterada, o elemento<code>&nbsp;</code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code></a><code> </code>deve ser utilizado, senão o elemento<code> </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a><code> </code>é adequado.</div>\n\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Categorias de conteúdo</a></dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\">Flutuante</a> e no caso dos elementos filhos de<code>&nbsp;&lt;ol&gt;&nbsp;</code>incluirem pelo menos um elemento de conteúdo <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/li\"><code>&lt;li&gt;</code></a> evidente.</li>\n <li><dfn>Conteúdo permitido</dfn> Zero ou mais elementos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/li\"><code>&lt;li&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><dfn>Omissão de etiqueta (<em>Tag</em>)</dfn> None, both the starting and ending tag are mandatory.</li>\n <li><dfn>Elementos pai permitidos </dfn> Qualquer elemento que aceite <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#flow content\">conteúdo flutuante</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Interface DOM</dfn> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLOListElement\"><code>HTMLOListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Este elemento inclui os&nbsp;</span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">atributos globais</a>.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"compact\"><a id=\"attr-compact\" href=\"#attr-compact\"><b><code>compact</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Este atributo boleano sugere que a lista deve ser renderizada em um estilo compacto. A interpretação deste atributo depende do perfil de navegação (<em>user agent</em>) e não funciona em todos os navegadores.&nbsp;<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><code>&nbsp;</code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code></a><code> </code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\" title=\"CSS\">CSS</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\" title=\"CSS\">CSS</a><code>&nbsp;</code><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/line-height\"><code>line-height</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a><code> </code><p>null</p></div></dd>\n <dt id=\"reversed\"><a id=\"attr-reversed\" href=\"#attr-reversed\"><b><code>reversed</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Este atributo boleano especifica que as partes desta lista serão especificadas em ordem reversa, isto é, a menos importante será listada primeiro.</dd>\n <dt id=\"start\"><a id=\"attr-start\" href=\"#attr-start\"><b><code>start</code></b></a><span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Este atributo inteiro especifica o valor inicial para a numeração dos itens da lista. Embora o tipo de ordenação dos elementos possa ser com algarismos romanos, tal como XXXI, ou letras, o valor inicial sempre é representado como um inteiro. Para iniciar a contagem a partir da letra \"C\", utilize<code> </code>&lt;ol start=\"3\"&gt;.\n <div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\"><strong>Nota</strong>: Este atributo, obsoleto na HTML4, foi reintroduzido na HTML5.</div>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"type\"><a id=\"attr-type\" href=\"#attr-type\"><b><code>type</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Indica o tipo de numeração:\n <ul>\n  <li><code>'a'</code> indica letras minúsculas,</li>\n  <li><code>'A'</code> indica letras maiúsculas,</li>\n  <li><code>'i'</code> indica algarismos romanos minúsculos,</li>\n  <li><code>'I'</code> indica algarismos romanos maiúsculos,</li>\n  <li>e <code>'1'</code> indica números (padrão).</li>\n </ul>\n\n <p>O tipo de marcação é usado na lista inteira,&nbsp;a menos que um atributo<code> </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/li#attr-type\"><code>type</code></a><code> </code>diferente seja utilizado dentro do elemento&nbsp;<code> </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/li\"><code>&lt;li&gt;</code></a>.</p>\n\n <div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect4\"><strong>Nota:&nbsp;</strong>Este atributo, obsoleto na HTML4, foi reintroduzido na HTML5. A menos que o valor do número na lista seja importante, a propriedade CSS<code>&nbsp;</code><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/list-style-type\"><code>list-style-type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a><code> </code>deve ser usada em seu lugar.</div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"simple_example","title":"Exemplo simples","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>primeiro item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>segundo item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>terceiro item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>A saída HTML acima será:</p>\n\n<ol>\n <li>primeiro item</li>\n <li>segundo item</li>\n <li>terceiro item</li>\n</ol>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usando_o_atributo_start","title":"Usando o atributo <em>start</em>","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">start</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>7<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>primeiro item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>segundo item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>terceiro item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>A saída HTML acima será:</p>\n\n<ol start=\"7\">\n <li>primeiro item</li>\n <li>segundo item</li>\n <li>terceiro item</li>\n</ol>","titleAsText":"Usando o atributo start"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"listas_aninhadas","title":"Listas aninhadas","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>primeiro item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>segundo item      <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Veja que a tag de fechamento &lt;/li&gt; não é colocada aqui! --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>segundo item primeiro subitem<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>segundo item segundo subitem<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>segundo item terceiro subitem<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>                <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Aqui está a tag de fechamento &lt;/li&gt; --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>terceiro item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>A saída HTML acima será:</p>\n\n<ol>\n <li>primeiro item</li>\n <li>segundo item\n  <ol>\n   <li>segundo item primeiro subitem</li>\n   <li>segundo item segundo subitem</li>\n   <li>segundo item terceiro&nbsp;subitem</li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n <li>terceiro item</li>\n</ol>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"<ol>_e_<ul>_aninhados","title":"&lt;ol&gt; e &lt;ul&gt; aninhados","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>primeiro item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>segundo item      <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Observe que a tag de fechamento &lt;/li&gt; não é colocada aqui! --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>segundo item primeiro subitem<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>segundo item segundo subitem<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>segundo item terceiro subitem<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>                <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Aqui está a tag de fechamento &lt;/li&gt; --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>terceiro item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>A saída HTML acima será:</p>\n\n<ol>\n <li>primeiro item</li>\n <li>segundo item\n  <ul>\n   <li style=\"list-style-type: square;\">segundo item primeiro subitem</li>\n   <li style=\"list-style-type: square;\">segundo item segundo subitem</li>\n   <li style=\"list-style-type: square;\">segundo item terceiro&nbsp;subitem</li>\n  </ul>\n </li>\n <li>terceiro item</li>\n</ol>","titleAsText":"<ol> e <ul> aninhados"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Situação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Observação</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/grouping-content.html#the-ol-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;ol&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/grouping-content.html#the-ol-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'HTMLOListElement' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/struct/lists.html#h-10.2\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;ol&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"compatibilidede_em_navegadores","title":"Compatibilidede em navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect5\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect6\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th><span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span>Característica</span></span></th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 or earlier)</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>atributo revertido</td>\n   <td>18</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/18\" title=\"Released on 2013-01-08.\">18.0</a> (18.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>5.2</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th><span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span>Característica</span></span></th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Móvel (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Móvel</th>\n   <th>Opera Móvel</th>\n   <th>Safari Móvel</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>atributo revertido</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>18.0 (18.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Outros elementos HTML relacionados à lista:<code> </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/li\"><code>&lt;li&gt;</code></a>,<code> </code><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/menu\"><code>&lt;menu&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a><code> </code>e o obsoleto<code> </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dir\"><code>&lt;dir&gt;</code></a>;</li>\n <li>Propriedades CSS que podem ser especialmente úteis para determinar o modelo do elemento<code>&nbsp;&lt;ol&gt;</code>:\n  <ul>\n   <li>a propriedade<code>&nbsp;</code><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/list-style\"><code>list-style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>,<code> </code><span class=\"st\">conveniente</span> para escolher a forma como os ordinais são exibidos,</li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Counter_Styles/Using_CSS_counters\" title=\"CSS_Counters\">contadores CSS</a>, útil para gerenciar listas&nbsp;complexas aninhadas,</li>\n   <li>a propriedade<code>&nbsp;</code><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/line-height\"><code>line-height</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>,<code> </code><span class=\"st\">proficiente</span> para simular o atributo obsoleto<code> </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol#attr-compact\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>compact</code></a>,</li>\n   <li>a propriedade<code> </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/margin\"><code>margin</code></a>,<code> </code><span class=\"st\">aplicável</span> para controlar a indentação da lista.</li>\n  </ul>\n </li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect7\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sumário","id":"sumário"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Compatibilidede em navegadores","id":"compatibilidede_em_navegadores"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O Elemento HTML <ol> (ou Elemento HTML de lista ordenada) representa uma lista de itens ordenados. De forma característica esses itens ordenados em uma lista são mostrados com uma contagem que os precede, que pode ser de qualquer tipo, como numerais, letras, algarismos romanos, ou simples símbolos. Esse modelo numerado não é definido na descrição html da página, mas na folha de estilos CSS associada, pela propriedade list-style-type (en-US).","popularity":0.002,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ol","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<ol>: The Ordered List element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ol","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<ol> : l'élément de liste ordonnée","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<ol>: 順序付きリスト要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<ol>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"ol","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<ol>: The Ordered List element","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<ol>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/element/ol","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/element/ol/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Elementos HTML"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol","title":"<ol>"}],"pageTitle":"<ol> - HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}